Don't tax my income then tax my spendatures, that is double taxation, no matter how you shake it up or how many times you make more taxation to hide a higher number.  It has been proven a flat tax (as dirra has explained) will do the same for governmental revenues AND will stop one of the biggest government money sinks, its called the IRS.<br>
