What spendatures, how about the pension and retirement plan those in public office get.  You know the one that says they can never draw from Social Security.  Yet read the fine print how they never pay into it, will never be a part of it, because after spending a particular base tenure of service they get a compensation package that STILL keeps them out of even the MIDDLE income bracket.  <br>
<br>
About guns, I am not a gun owner, never will be.  But if you step into my house, I promise you, either you or I will leave in a body bag.  And for the mere fact that can happen, every American has the right to bare arms.  We have violent enemies, both foreign and domestic, I wouldn't shed a tear for either that died defiling the soveriegn rights of my fellow Americans.<br>
<br>
I am a bad American, and damn proud of it.<br>
