And the education thing is easy.<br>
<br>
The feds fund education so that each child, no matter where they are located, has the opportunity to receive a certain level of education.<br>
<br>
If the responsibilty of funding education was left entirely to the local area, you would have really smart kids in California where a large number of people can easily bear the burden of public education, and you would have really stupid fucks in Maine, when the population could not support the same cost burden.<br>
